data.description: **OFFERS DEADLINE MONDAY 4/29/24 at 12:00PM** HIDDEN GEM IN THIS DESIRABLE COMMUNITY OF GLENWOOD HEIGHTS!  SPACIOUS NORTHWEST FACING 1750 SQ.FT. QUAD LEVEL WITH 4 BED / 2 FULL BATH SITUATED ON A PREMIUM 0.28 ACRE COURT LOT W/EXPANSIVE BACKYARD & TREE-LINED VIEW BACKING TO LOWER ROUGE PARKWAY.   BRICK-PAVER WALKWAY GUIDES YOU TO THE ENTRY WAY WELCOMING YOU TO AN OPEN-CONCEPT 1ST FLOOR LIVING ROOM W/CROWN MOLDINGS & NEW LIGHT FIXTURES CURRENTLY USED AS A DINING ROOM.   PLENTY OF CULINARY PREP SPACE & STORAGE IN KITCHEN W/PAINTED CABINETS & NEWER MICROWAVE W/NOOK OFFERING ADDL. SPACE TO GATHER OR USE AS A WORK/SCHOOL DROP ZONE.  UPPER LEVEL YOU WILL FIND FULL BATH W/DOUBLE SINKS, UPDATED BRUSHED SATIN FAUCETS, PENDANT LIGHTING & CERAMIC TILE FLOORS.  PRIMARY BEDROOM TASTEFULLY UPDATED W/ NEW CARPET & ACCENT WALL, CEILING FAN & WALK-IN CLOSET.  ADDITIONAL 2 BEDROOMS BOTH OFFER CEILING FANS & MODERN GREY TONES.  LOWER LEVEL PROVIDES AMPLE ENTERTAINING SPACE IN FAMILY ROOM W/NEW CARPET, NEW RECESSED LIGHTING (2021) & WALL MOUNTED TV ABOVE NATURAL GAS FIREPLACE.  LOWER FULL BATH HAS BEEN UPDATED W/VINYL FLOOR, NEW VANITY, NEW LIGHT FIXTURES & FRESH PAINT (2022).  LOWER LEVEL BEDROOM CURRENTLY BEING USED AS AN OFFICE.  ENJOY THE PEACE & TRANQUILITY OF THE BACKYARD W/COVERED GAZEBO. NEWER CONCRETE DRIVEWAY & PARKING PAD (2017) OFFERS ACCESS TO REAR-FACING GARAGE.  OTHER UPDATES INCLUDE HOT WATER TANK (2023), VINYL WINDOWS (2020), VINYL SIDING & TRIM (2020), CARPETING & PADDING (2020), ROOF (2017), FURNACE, AC & HUMIDIFIER (2016).  THIS HAS THE VIEWS, LOCATION, SPACE AND UPDATES NEEDED TO CALL HOME.  SCHEDULE TODAY!!
